metadata.description: Processed Mars surface imagery for deep-zoom exploration and feature labeling

big_sky.description: Large portions of Martian sky, often showing atmospheric conditions
big_sky.scientific_interest: Atmospheric studies, dust storms, weather patterns

close_up_rock.description: Detailed views of individual rocks and geological formations
close_up_rock.scientific_interest: Rock composition, weathering patterns, geological history

crater.description: Impact craters of various sizes on the Martian surface
crater.scientific_interest: Impact history, crater formation, geological dating

distant_horizon.description: Distant Martian landscape features and horizon views

drift.scientific_interest: Aeolian processes, wind patterns, sediment transport

drill_hole.description: Holes drilled by Curiosity for sample collection
drill_hole.scientific_interest: Subsurface composition, sample analysis, drilling success

dune.description: Sand dunes formed by wind action
dune.scientific_interest: Aeolian processes, sand migration, surface dynamics

edge.description: Edges of rocks, cliffs, or geological boundaries
edge.scientific_interest: Geological boundaries, erosion patterns, structural analysis

embankment.description: Raised areas or embankments in the terrain
embankment.scientific_interest: Geological formation, erosion resistance, structural geology

other.description: Miscellaneous features not fitting other categories
other.scientific_interest: Various phenomena, unusual features, classification challenges

outcrop.description: Exposed rock formations and geological outcrops
outcrop.scientific_interest: Rock layers, geological history, sedimentary structures

pavement.scientific_interest: Surface processes, rock weathering, thermal cycling

rover.description: Parts of the Curiosity rover visible in images

sand.description: Sandy surfaces and loose sediment areas
sand.scientific_interest: Sediment composition, grain size, surface mobility

stone.description: Individual stones and small rock fragments
stone.scientific_interest: Rock fragments, transport processes, composition variety

track.description: Wheel tracks left by the Curiosity rover
track.scientific_interest: Rover mobility, surface interaction, terrain analysis

wheel.description: Curiosity rover wheels visible in images
wheel.scientific_interest: Rover status, wheel wear, mobility assessment
